Package: GIFTr
Type: Package
Title: GIFT Questions Format Generator From Dataframes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Omar I. Elashkar  <omar.ibrahim@miuegypt.edu.eg>
Maintainer: Omar I. Elashkar <omar.ibrahim@miuegypt.edu.eg>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: stringr, glue
Description: GIFTr package in intended to help course creators to upload
    questions to MOODLE and other LMS for quizzes. GIFTr takes dataframe or tibble of questions of
    four types: mcq, numerical questions, true or false and short answer,and export it a text 
    file formatted in MOODLe GIFT format. You can prepare a spreadsheet in any software and import 
    it in R and generate any number of questions with HTML, markdown and LATEX support.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
URL: https://github.com/omarelashkar/GIFTr
Suggests: 
    knitr,
